   Welcome to the U.S. Capitol Virtual Tour -- an interactive, user
   friendly, multimedia presentation of the U.S. Capitol.
   Experience panorama views and discover historical information about the
   rooms and artifacts of the U.S. Capitol.
   This tour will leave you with the feel of an actual visit to the U.S.
   Capitol and serve as a unique "Capitol" experience.
